{"tid":577602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[古惑的印印] 裝CAM再主動挑釁激到廢老出手打佢！","createTime":"2018-03-02T01:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T02:12:01.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc9e291c9ff9087374885ee473c5d55f7b35654","tid":577602,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:52:09.000Z","msg":"一段印傭疑遭講廣東話老僱主掌摑和扼頸的片段，今日在網上瘋傳，該片威力驚人更衝出國際，就連遠至英國的《Time News International 》fb亦有轉載。片段可見，一名滿頭白髮的婆婆，疑不滿女傭的工作表現，二人發生口角，其後因女傭不斷駁嘴，令婆婆大受刺激，繼而做出掌摑及扼女傭頸的行為，更怒罵「我要謀殺你」、「我要同你一齊死」！據知，片段是女傭開fb 網上直播，立即引來印傭界極大迴響，因而火速瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180301/large/1519908984_816d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180301%2Flarge%2F1519908984_816d.jpg&h=d39c6229&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n由於片中的背景疑似香港的公屋或舊樓單位，加上老僱主操廣東話，以及印傭亦曾以廣東話「駁嘴」，故有網民推斷，肇事的地點為香港。警方發言人稱，關注互聯網上流傳一段家庭傭工懷疑被襲擊的片段，網絡安全及科技罪案調查科正了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180301/57892292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180301%2F57892292&d=tzihyB9kHcV2KeLkcst4skbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=1b57134c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180301%2F57892292&h=095fe7c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180301/57892292</a>"},{"pid":"a45172f2f5aac66d7138dcbf585a24391f4f0724","tid":577602,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"片中，起初婆婆質問女傭：「我係咪對你好差？你講一句，問良心！」女傭卻大吐苦水，反駁小小事都會被罵，「永遠都係婆婆啱&hellip;&hellip;我唔知婆婆做乜。」婆婆勃然大怒指着女傭：「你激到我好火滾呀，我未試過用傭工用到好似你咁」，其間女傭繼續駁嘴：「我未試過好似婆婆咁㗎！」婆婆聽罷隨即要求她自行辭職，「你走囉，咁淒涼咪辭職囉」，惟女傭斷言拒絕，「我唔會辭職㗎。」<br />\n<br />\n兩人的爭吵未見平息，婆婆不斷指罵女傭：「你唔好激到我咁火滾呀！」惟女傭卻指：「你自己激，唔係我！」婆婆聞言更火上加油，直呼：「你激呀，激我激成咁樣，你顧住最收尾嗰兩年，你做埋啲咁陰質嘢，蝦老人家，不得好死」；其間婆婆更將女傭推倒在床上並多次掌摑其手及臉部。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">女傭在片中一度以印尼語表示：「婆婆係啲咁嘅人，佢真係好衰，佢鬧一陣就會停，佢不嬲都係咁」。</span>婆婆的情緒越來越激動，一邊罵着女傭，一邊用力扼着女傭的頸部大罵：「你做乜講印尼文，鬧我乜嘢」，「我要謀殺你」，「我要同你一齊死！」但女傭不甘示弱，稱「殺咪殺囉！」片段最後所見女傭被多次掌摑及掐頸，臉部已經紅腫。最後，女傭滿面淚痕，照鏡檢查傷勢，又一邊用手掩著嘴，<span style=\"color: red;\">向著鏡頭用印尼語表示：「你睇吓，婆婆打成我咁樣」。</span>"},{"pid":"dd798032d24bd0152bc566c97fd9ae9613097f14","tid":577602,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:53:42.000Z","msg":"【23:54】警方晚上在黃大仙區拘捕一名79歲姓彭女子，懷疑她昨日曾襲擊及言語恐嚇一名35歲外籍女子，案件列作普通襲擊及刑事恐嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，黃大仙警區刑事調查隊第六隊接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n【08:45更新】彭婦經調查後，已獲准保釋候查，下周初向警方報到。"},{"pid":"337eca683b07c2b1d769707389a84a1ae5f8058c","tid":577602,"uid":35870,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:55:06.000Z","msg":"個呀婆又係on9<br />\n出手打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde8799e27a9dd6317fe6a6a306ae0f7e67bbba5","tid":577602,"uid":168506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:55:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdc3e0de8480cc250683fd06f70c1f913f74fe79","tid":577602,"uid":41737,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adf959bd3421e766ef20966c4ec9c5ae27a97977","tid":577602,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"337eca683b07c2b1d769707389a84a1ae5f8058c","tid":577602,"uid":35870,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:55:06.000Z","msg":"個呀婆又係on9<br />\n出手打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"可能就係知道廢老易畀人激，所以激多佢兩錢重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42b08582664d5a6f0b3569aefa400855d5ac77e0","tid":577602,"uid":166663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:01:08.000Z","msg":"有晒片﹐仲鋤唔死件廢老。<br />\n支持告到件廢老坐監。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a9d1242ac9e943ef078088e98300a57ef73408","tid":577602,"uid":35870,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"adf959bd3421e766ef20966c4ec9c5ae27a97977","tid":577602,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"337eca683b07c2b1d769707389a84a1ae5f8058c","tid":577602,"uid":35870,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T01:55:06.000Z","msg":"個呀婆又係on9<br />\n出手打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:00:08.000Z","msg":"可能就係知道廢老易畀人激，所以激多佢兩錢重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"應該唔係第一次，知道佢會出手打人，所以放部cam係到伏佢<br />\n不過個工人都有d鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢事跟車太貼"},{"pid":"fa047d4a10b426fa70014865ded27452e9575212","tid":577602,"uid":73089,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"保持兩秒距離 有時啲賓妹都好古猾"},{"pid":"348e604c5ec6237bac9c664796b9010a6405067f","tid":577602,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0b2d94b6a9d2bf97c04d41552618c8ea1b080865","tid":577602,"uid":67346,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"348e604c5ec6237bac9c664796b9010a6405067f","tid":577602,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"我地睇嘅係客觀事實<br />\n件廢老有打人捉到正就係證據<br />\n佢之前有乜鳩委屈就應該另外睇<br />\n肯用下腦洗乜驚炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831d60e2d4353ab0b26c03713904bb592113ae03","tid":577602,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T01:28:20.000Z","msg":"如果當場激死左個阿婆 <br />\n條直播片就作繭自縛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a060d16f78af315f5e5b97dadf57195535f5b281","tid":577602,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T01:40:55.000Z","msg":"廢老唔啱但我都唔會撑隻南亞雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f45b068cd8670260b7f0413d272dcd6d9b715e7","tid":577602,"uid":23815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a060d16f78af315f5e5b97dadf57195535f5b281","tid":577602,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T01:40:55.000Z","msg":"廢老唔啱但我都唔會撑隻南亞雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T01:43:52.000Z","msg":"Agger<br />\nOn9"},{"pid":"08fcf94cacb4601dff364b4b26bd6664b3babe73","tid":577602,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T01:50:18.000Z","msg":"啲廢老又話食鹽多過你食米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來咁撚ON9"},{"pid":"536756b247c952774e6842cae47683ec642c6eab","tid":577602,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"廢老特別易燥"}]}